{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_24","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc \"cd apps/waketask-iphone && sed -n '1,220p' SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/Resources/privacy.md && sed -n '1,220p' SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/Resources/terms.md\"","aggregated_output":"# Privacy Policy\n\n**Last Updated:** October 8, 2025\n\n## Information We Collect\n- Account info (email, name)\n- Usage data\n- AI conversations\n- Device info\n\n## How We Use It\n- Provide services\n- Process AI requests\n- Improve app\n- Send notifications\n\n## Data Sharing\n- **AI Providers:** Your prompts go to AI services (OpenAI, Anthropic)\n- **Analytics:** Anonymous usage stats\n- **Apple:** Payment processing\n\n## Your Rights\n- Access your data\n- Delete your account\n- Export conversations\n- Opt-out of marketing\n\n## Security\n- Encryption in transit\n- Secure storage\n- Regular audits\n\n## Children\nNot for users under 13.\n\n## Changes\nWe'll notify you of policy updates.\n\n## Contact\nEmail: privacy@yourapp.com\n\n## GDPR (EU)\nYou have right to data portability, erasure, and complaint filing.\n\n## CCPA (California)\nWe don't sell your data. Contact us for data disclosure.\n\n*Customize this policy with legal counsel.*\n\n# Terms of Service\n\n**Last Updated:** October 8, 2025\n\n## 1. Acceptance of Terms\nBy using this app, you agree to these terms.\n\n## 2. Use License\nPersonal, non-commercial use only.\n\n## 3. User Accounts\nYou are responsible for your account security.\n\n## 4. AI Content\nAI-generated content may not always be accurate. Verify important information.\n\n## 5. Privacy\nSee our Privacy Policy for data handling practices.\n\n## 6. Prohibited Uses\nNo illegal, harmful, or abusive content generation.\n\n## 7. Subscription\nSubscriptions auto-renew. Fees are non-refundable except as required by law.\n\n## 8. Termination\nWe may terminate accounts for Terms violations.\n\n## 9. Limitation of Liability\nWe are not liable for damages from app use.\n\n## 10. Changes\nWe may update these terms. Continued use = acceptance.\n\n## Contact\nEmail: support@yourapp.com\n\n*Consult legal counsel to customize for your needs.*\n\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
